articles.author: Sam Meredith
articles.title: Georgia president holds talks on 'how to save' the country as U.S., EU and NATO decry 'Russian law' - CNBC
articles.description: The U.S., European Union, NATO and the United Nations have all issued statements expressing concern about Georgia's divisive legislation.
